title: Depeche Mode - Behind the Wheel, Route 66, remixes
description:
I used to obsess about these songs like no other.  The Megamix is one of the finest 12" singles ever in the history of the (sounds of the) universe.  I've gathered these from various releases.  All are digital sources except the Megadub which came from vinyl I think.

Tonight, I'm in the hands of fate
